org.jetel.ctl.extensions

Class IntegralLib

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.ctl.extensions.TLFunctionLibrary
      • org.jetel.ctl.extensions.IntegralLib
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITLFunctionLibrary

    public class IntegralLib
extends TLFunctionLibrary
    These functions have to be part of core engine plugin, since can be invoked direct from CTL executor. For example function copyByName() function is directly used for evaluation of 'record1.* = record2.*' assignment expression.
